## Using These Templates

1. Choose the appropriate template based on encounter type
2. Fill in all relevant sections before the session
3. Use quick reference sections during gameplay
4. Update related templates after the encounter

## Tips for Encounter Management

### Combat Encounters
* Pre-roll initiative for NPCs/monsters
* Have stat blocks ready
* Track resource usage
* Note environmental factors

### Social Encounters
* Prepare NPC motivations
* List possible conversation paths
* Note important information to reveal
* Track relationship changes

### Dungeon Encounters
* Map out areas in advance
* Place monsters strategically
* Consider escape routes
* Plan treasure placement

